Features of the Dashboard:
2021-2022 Sales Trend Analysis: Visual representation of sales trends across months, comparing 2021 and 2022.
Key Metrics Visualization:
Total Sales
Profit
Number of Customers
Customer Satisfaction Metrics: Includes quality, hygiene, service, availability, and speed.
Geographical Distribution: Sales distribution by country on a map of South America

Purpose
This dashboard serves as a tool for tracking performance, understanding trends, and identifying opportunities for growth in South American markets.
